00:15:23,120 --> 00:15:26,110
Mampus, berengsek.
Ayo, berengsek.

253
00:15:29,940 --> 00:15:31,760
Oraoraoraora!

254
00:15:34,880 --> 00:15:36,590
Selanjutnya siapa?!

255
00:15:39,700 --> 00:15:40,870
Maju sini!

256
00:15:52,750 --> 00:15:53,920
Bang Draken!

257
00:15:54,060 --> 00:15:55,470
Bang Draken!

258
00:15:57,530 --> 00:15:59,400
Kenapa kau malah melamun?!

259
00:15:59,640 --> 00:16:00,560
Maaf.

260
00:16:19,360 --> 00:16:20,960
Sialan!

261
00:16:21,820 --> 00:16:23,750
Ujung-ujungnya tidak berhasil.

262
00:16:25,510 --> 00:16:27,280
Pada perseteruan hari ini,

263
00:16:27,360 --> 00:16:31,000
pasti Bang Draken bakalan
dibunuh oleh Bang Kiyomasa.

264
00:16:32,120 --> 00:16:33,190
Aku ...

265
00:16:33,300 --> 00:16:36,700
... harus melindungi Bang Draken
di masa lalu kali ini!

266
00:16:37,650 --> 00:16:39,860
Aku tak ingin melihatnya lagi.

267
00:16:39,900 --> 00:16:41,600
Melihat kematian Akkun.

268
00:16:41,640 --> 00:16:43,210
Dan juga kematian Hina!

269
00:16:53,430 --> 00:16:55,330
Aku harus menghentikan Bang Kiyomasa.

270
00:16:56,160 --> 00:16:57,360
Aku akan ...

271
