Mikey.

282
00:18:05,080 --> 00:18:06,490
Itu pemimpinnya.

283
00:18:06,720 --> 00:18:08,180
Ayo habisi.

284
00:18:08,520 --> 00:18:11,780
"Mikey Tak Terkalahkan"
enggak ada apa-apanya!

285
00:18:15,730 --> 00:18:16,480
Peh!

286
00:18:16,800 --> 00:18:18,540
Kenapa kau menyerang Kenchin?!

287
00:18:19,400 --> 00:18:20,400
Berengsek!

288
00:18:23,160 --> 00:18:25,600
Kau tahu kalau aku dan Kenchin
sudah berdamai, 'kan?!

289
00:18:29,120 --> 00:18:30,980
Tapi kau menggunakan Moebius.

290
00:18:31,060 --> 00:18:33,280
Jangan pakai cara kotor!

291
00:18:35,310 --> 00:18:37,920
Jangan seenaknya berdamai!

292
00:18:38,060 --> 00:18:40,260
Aku tidak terima!

293
00:18:40,610 --> 00:18:42,470
Persoalan Pa sudah beres.

294
00:18:42,480 --> 00:18:43,660
Belum beres!

295
00:18:53,120 --> 00:18:56,830
Padahal Pachin tertangkap,
tapi semua beres begitu saja?

296
00:18:57,380 --> 00:18:59,030
Tidak lucu!

297
00:18:59,840 --> 00:19:02,140
Hanya beginilah caranya!

298
00:19:02,610 --> 00:19:04,050
Pachin itu ...

299
00:19:04,080 --> 00:19:06,480
... segalanya bagiku!

300
00:19:08,860 --> 00:19:11,310
Kalau Touman menelantarkan Pachin,

301
00:19:11,860 --> 00:19:14,720
maka harus kumusuhi, 'kan?!

302
00:19:15,080 --> 00:19:16,740
Maju sini, Mikey!

303
00:19:18,000 --> 00:19:20,350
Kenapa kau tak membalas tinjuku?!

304
00:19:20,380 --> 00:19:22,280
Satu tinjumu pasti langsung mengalahkanku!

305
00:19:27,980 --> 00:19:29,390
Lihatlah aku.

306
00:19:33,600 --> 00:19:35,240
Apa aku tertawa?

307
00:19:36,860 --> 00:19:38,580
Apa aku tertawa ...

308
00:19:38,980 --> 00:19:40,450
... atas tertangkapnya Pachin?

309
00:19:41,680 --> 00:19:42,770
Menyakitkan, tahu.

310
00:19:45,320 --> 00:19:47,210
Kalau aku dan Kenchin berseteru,

311
00:19:47,220 --> 00:19:49,910
lalu Touman tercerai-berai,
itu akan menyedihkan.

312
00:19:50,360 --> 00:19:52,060
Takemicchi bilang begitu.

313
00:19:54,120 --> 00:19:56,190
Aku tidak kepikiran ...

314
00:19:57,200 --> 00:19:59,690
... kalau semuanya akan berseteru.

315
00:20:02,150 --> 00:20:05,010
Pukullah aku hingga kau puas, Pehyan.

316
00:20:06,460 --> 00:20:07,630
Mikey.

317
00:20:08,800 --> 00:20:10,150
Aku ...

318
00:20:10,860 --> 00:20:12,670
... tidak ingin berseteru denganmu.

319
00:20:14,620 --> 00:20:16,840
Jadi, anggaplah semuanya ini selesai,

320
00:20:16,960 --> 00:20:18,250
dan kembalilah,

321
00:20:19,000 --> 00:20:19,780
Pehyan.

322
00:20:37,520 --> 00:20:38,790
Bang Draken!

323
00:20:39,840 --> 00:20:40,880
Bang Draken!

324
00:20:41,180 --> 00:20:42,440
Oke!

325
00:20:44,300 --> 00:20:45,500
Maju sini!

326
00:20:45,520 --> 00:20:47,500
Padahal lagi buru-buru!

327
00:20:55,420 --> 00:20:58,180
Sialaaaaan!

328
00:21:00,060 --> 00:21:01,680
Baik Bang Draken,

329
00:21:01,680 --> 00:21:04,110
maupun Bang Kiyomasa,
tidak kutemukan.

330
00:21:04,600 --> 00:21:07,340
Mereka berdua pergi ke mana?!

331
00:21:17,020 --> 00:21:17,640
Ah.

332
00:21:19,460 --> 00:21:20,360
Itu dia!

333
00:21:22,080 --> 00:21:24,650
Ketemu juga kau,
Bang Kiyomasa!

334
00:21:25,940 --> 00:21:29,440
Aku akan membunuh Draken.

335
00:21:30,260 --> 00:21:32,240
Aku pasti akan menghentikannya!

336
00:21:34,360 --> 00:21:34,960
Hah?

337
00:21:35,880 --> 00:21:36,810
HAH?!

338
00:21:39,720 --> 00:21:40,540
Eh?

339
00:21:41,780 --> 00:21:45,160
Berhasil.
Aku berhasil melakukannya!

340
00:21:54,980 --> 00:21:55,790
Hah?!

341
00:21:58,560 --> 00:21:59,900
Draken!

342
00:22:00,600 --> 00:22:01,470
Draken!

343
00:22:02,000 --> 00:22:03,430
Bang Draken!

344
00:22:06,600 --> 00:22:08,300
Bang Draken!

345
00:22:21,040 --> 00:22:26,880
Dengan berjalan di sisimu yang
agak bau keringat

346
00:22:26,900 --> 00:22:29,790
itu sudah cukup bagiku

347
00:22:30,030 --> 00:22:35,810
Seraya dihantam oleh hujan tiba-tiba,

348
00:22:35,820 --> 00:22:39,320
kita bercumbu di tengah dinginnya malam

349
00:22:41,220 --> 00:22:49,070
Kala aku berpaling, masihlah ada
diriku yang kerap tertawa

350
00:22:49,120 --> 00:22:50,250
Tolonglah!

351
00:22:50,270 --> 00:22:57,220
Hei, ayo menuju masa depan yang
tak mungkin terwujud!

352
00:22:57,260 --> 00:22:59,710
Bawalah aku sekarang juga

353
00:22:59,730 --> 00:23:01,720
ke dunia baru

354
00:23:01,730 --> 00:23:06,440
olehmu yang kusebut sebagai "pahlawanku"

355
00:23:06,440 --> 00:23:08,450
Harapan yang blak-blakan

356
00:23:08,470 --> 00:23:10,760
melampaui waktu yang terhenti

357
00:23:10,820 --> 00:23:15,710
"Tiada lagi yang kubutuhkan selainmu"

358
00:23:15,750 --> 00:23:23,590
Aku akan selalu bernapas di sini

359
00:23:29,930 --> 00:23:32,100
Hancurkan jarum yang bengkok

360
00:23:32,160 --> 00:23:34,400
dengan suara tegas

361
00:23:34,410 --> 00:23:36,810
lalu empaskan takdir!


